    <p style="position:absolute;top:1074px;left:478px;white-space:nowrap" class="ft210"><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/standard-assessment-procedure#:~:text=For%20existing%20buildings%2C%20a%20simplified,time%20the%20building%20was%20constructed.">&#160;</a></p>
